name: Besin Ka Omelette Recipe | Shireen Anwar | Masala TV
ingredients: Ingredients for Besin Ka Omelette Recipe: Eggs 3 Gram flour (roasted) 2 tbsp Garlic Powder ¼ tsp Black Pepper Powder ½ tsp Salt ½ tsp Cumin Seeds ½ tsp Red Pepper (crushed) ½ tsp Onions (chopped) 2 tbsp Green Chilies (chopped) 2
instructions: Whisk all the ingredients together. Heat quarter cup oil in a fry pan Fry like a pan cake from both sides. Serve hot.
